    "deckId": "wine-vocab",
    "frontText": "Peppery",
    "backText": "A spicy sensation, specifically black pepper or white pepper. Signature trait of Syrah/Shiraz (black pepper from the compound rotundone), Grüner Veltliner (white pepper), and Grenache.\n\n**Usage:** \"Classic Northern Rhône Syrah — cracked black pepper and dark fruit.\"",
    "hint": "Crack the pepper grinder over your glass 🫑",
    "difficulty": 2,
